{
  "video_id": "_B1JmOerYmY",
  "title": "Why I speak up about living with epilepsy | Sitawa Wafula",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12605.0,
      "end_time": 14832.0,
      "text": "I have a confession."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16858.0,
      "end_time": 19305.0,
      "text": "I have been in an affair"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19329.0,
      "end_time": 21532.0,
      "text": "since I was 17 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22704.0,
      "end_time": 26551.0,
      "text": "I wish I could talk about butterflies in my stomach"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26575.0,
      "end_time": 29413.0,
      "text": "or maps I drew on the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29438.0,
      "end_time": 31723.0,
      "text": "when I think about this affair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31747.0,
      "end_time": 33166.0,
      "text": "but I cannot."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33896.0,
      "end_time": 37156.0,
      "text": "I wish I could talk about sweet words spoken"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37180.0,
      "end_time": 39253.0,
      "text": "or gifts that I received"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39277.0,
      "end_time": 40997.0,
      "text": "from this affair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41210.0,
      "end_time": 42497.0,
      "text": "but I cannot."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43738.0,
      "end_time": 46917.0,
      "text": "All I can tell you about is the aftermath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47742.0,
      "end_time": 51494.0,
      "text": "about days I spent constantly asking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51518.0,
      "end_time": 54891.0,
      "text": "Why, why, why me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57240.0,
      "end_time": 59385.0,
      "text": "I remember how it all began."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60880.0,
      "end_time": 62875.0,
      "text": "I was in my final year of high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62899.0,
      "end_time": 66220.0,
      "text": "and my class had just won in sports,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66460.0,
      "end_time": 70765.0,
      "text": "so we were singing and dancing and hugging each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70789.0,
      "end_time": 72573.0,
      "text": "I went and took a shower."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72597.0,
      "end_time": 74181.0,
      "text": "Then I went for dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75610.0,
      "end_time": 77311.0,
      "text": "And when I sat down to eat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77335.0,
      "end_time": 79884.0,
      "text": "my teeth started chattering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79909.0,
      "end_time": 82444.0,
      "text": "and so I couldn&#39;t put the spoon in my mouth."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82468.0,
      "end_time": 85220.0,
      "text": "I rushed to the nurse&#39;s office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85460.0,
      "end_time": 88222.0,
      "text": "and because I couldn&#39;t talk, I just pointed at my mouth."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88984.0,
      "end_time": 90770.0,
      "text": "She didn&#39;t know what was happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90794.0,
      "end_time": 92878.0,
      "text": "so she told me to lie down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92902.0,
      "end_time": 94174.0,
      "text": "and it worked --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94198.0,
      "end_time": 96660.0,
      "text": "after a few minutes, the chattering stopped."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96685.0,
      "end_time": 101113.0,
      "text": "I was about to dash out, and she told me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101137.0,
      "end_time": 105267.0,
      "text": "no, she insisted -- that I go up to the dormitories to sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106850.0,
      "end_time": 109202.0,
      "text": "Here I was in my final year of high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109226.0,
      "end_time": 113781.0,
      "text": "just a few months from doing my end of high school exams"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113805.0,
      "end_time": 118694.0,
      "text": "and a few days from doing a set of exams we call here in Kenya \"mocks,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118718.0,
      "end_time": 124399.0,
      "text": "which are somehow meant to gauge how prepared one is for the final exams."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 124423.0,
      "end_time": 126715.0,
      "text": "There is no way I was going to sleep"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126739.0,
      "end_time": 129183.0,
      "text": "and let a set of exams mock me."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129207.0,
      "end_time": 132209.0,
      "text": "I went to class, sat down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132234.0,
      "end_time": 134589.0,
      "text": "took my Kenyan history notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134613.0,
      "end_time": 138378.0,
      "text": "and there I was, down Kenyan coastal town,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138402.0,
      "end_time": 140885.0,
      "text": "with the great Mekatilili wa Menza,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140909.0,
      "end_time": 145906.0,
      "text": "the Giriama woman who led her people against British colonial rule."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 147319.0,
      "end_time": 150234.0,
      "text": "Then, without any notice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 150259.0,
      "end_time": 153350.0,
      "text": "my left hand started jerking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 154375.0,
      "end_time": 157111.0,
      "text": "and it was as if I was marking imaginary papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 157893.0,
      "end_time": 160299.0,
      "text": "In and out it went,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160953.0,
      "end_time": 164148.0,
      "text": "and with every stroke, one by one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 164172.0,
      "end_time": 167655.0,
      "text": "my classmates stopped concentrating on their reading"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 167679.0,
      "end_time": 169713.0,
      "text": "and started looking at me."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 170376.0,
      "end_time": 173470.0,
      "text": "And I tried really hard to stop it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 173710.0,
      "end_time": 174727.0,
      "text": "but I couldn&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 174751.0,
      "end_time": 176801.0,
      "text": "because it had a life of its own."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 178107.0,
      "end_time": 182728.0,
      "text": "And then, when it was sure everybody was looking at us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182753.0,
      "end_time": 186942.0,
      "text": "in its final show and official introduction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 186967.0,
      "end_time": 189776.0,
      "text": "I had my first full-blown seizure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189800.0,
      "end_time": 194953.0,
      "text": "which was the beginning of what has been a 15-year-long affair."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 197361.0,
      "end_time": 203916.0,
      "text": "Seizures are the trademark characteristic for most types of epilepsy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 203940.0,
      "end_time": 208418.0,
      "text": "and every first-ever seizure needs to be assessed by a doctor"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 208442.0,
      "end_time": 210945.0,
      "text": "to determine if one has epilepsy"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 210969.0,
      "end_time": 213655.0,
      "text": "or if it&#39;s a symptom of something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 213679.0,
      "end_time": 217535.0,
      "text": "In my case, it was confirmed that I had epilepsy."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 218910.0,
      "end_time": 222986.0,
      "text": "I spent a large chunk of my time in hospital and at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 223100.0,
      "end_time": 226295.0,
      "text": "and only went back to do my final exams."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 227255.0,
      "end_time": 231103.0,
      "text": "I had seizures in between papers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 231128.0,
      "end_time": 233263.0,
      "text": "but managed to get good enough grades"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 233288.0,
      "end_time": 236548.0,
      "text": "to be admitted for an actuarial science degree"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 236572.0,
      "end_time": 238163.0,
      "text": "at the University of Nairobi."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 238187.0,
      "end_time": 241635.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 244530.0,
      "end_time": 249930.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I had to drop out in my second year."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 249117.0,
      "end_time": 251560.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t have good enough coping skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 251584.0,
      "end_time": 253720.0,
      "text": "and a support community around me."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 254315.0,
      "end_time": 256225.0,
      "text": "I was lucky enough to get a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 257500.0,
      "end_time": 261734.0,
      "text": "but I was fired from that job when I had a seizure in the workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 262521.0,
      "end_time": 266645.0,
      "text": "So I found myself in a space"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 266669.0,
      "end_time": 270101.0,
      "text": "where I was constantly asking myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 270125.0,
      "end_time": 272596.0,
      "text": "why this had to happen to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 273548.0,
      "end_time": 276406.0,
      "text": "I lived in denial for a long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 277264.0,
      "end_time": 284125.0,
      "text": "and the denial was maybe because of the things that had happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 284149.0,
      "end_time": 286869.0,
      "text": "dropping out of school and being fired from my job."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 287523.0,
      "end_time": 291538.0,
      "text": "Or maybe it was because of the things I had heard about epilepsy"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 291562.0,
      "end_time": 294147.0,
      "text": "and about people living with epilepsy:"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 294171.0,
      "end_time": 296403.0,
      "text": "that they would never live on their own;"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 296427.0,
      "end_time": 298668.0,
      "text": "that they would never travel on their own"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 298692.0,
      "end_time": 300112.0,
      "text": "or even get work;"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 301191.0,
      "end_time": 303390.0,
      "text": "that they were outcasts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 303640.0,
      "end_time": 306887.0,
      "text": "with a spirit in them that they needed to be delivered from."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 308482.0,
      "end_time": 312109.0,
      "text": "And so the more I thought about these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 312133.0,
      "end_time": 315810.0,
      "text": "the more my seizures became,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 315834.0,
      "end_time": 318939.0,
      "text": "and I spent days with my legs locked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 318963.0,
      "end_time": 322384.0,
      "text": "my speech became blurred"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 322408.0,
      "end_time": 326690.0,
      "text": "and on days on end, this is how I&#39;d be."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 326867.0,
      "end_time": 328900.0,
      "text": "Two or three days after a seizure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 328924.0,
      "end_time": 332154.0,
      "text": "my head and my hand would still be twitching."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 334790.0,
      "end_time": 335683.0,
      "text": "I felt lost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 336500.0,
      "end_time": 338444.0,
      "text": "like I&#39;d lost everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 339353.0,
      "end_time": 340810.0,
      "text": "and sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 342596.0,
      "end_time": 344315.0,
      "text": "even the will to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 353544.0,
      "end_time": 354885.0,
      "text": "(Sigh)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 360377.0,
      "end_time": 362912.0,
      "text": "I had so much frustration in me."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 363821.0,
      "end_time": 365368.0,
      "text": "And so I started writing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 365392.0,
      "end_time": 368231.0,
      "text": "because the people around me didn&#39;t have answers"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 368255.0,
      "end_time": 370210.0,
      "text": "to the questions that I had."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 370929.0,
      "end_time": 373631.0,
      "text": "And so I wrote my fears"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 373655.0,
      "end_time": 374955.0,
      "text": "and my doubts."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 375749.0,
      "end_time": 380160.0,
      "text": "I wrote about my good days and my bad days and my really ugly days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 380400.0,
      "end_time": 381790.0,
      "text": "and I shared them on a blog."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 382898.0,
      "end_time": 384236.0,
      "text": "And before long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 385308.0,
      "end_time": 388938.0,
      "text": "I began to be seen and heard by people who had epilepsy"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 388963.0,
      "end_time": 390397.0,
      "text": "and their families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 390421.0,
      "end_time": 393257.0,
      "text": "and even those who did not have the diagnosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 393773.0,
      "end_time": 397863.0,
      "text": "And I moved from that girl who constantly asked why me"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 397887.0,
      "end_time": 400674.0,
      "text": "to one who not only self-advocates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 400698.0,
      "end_time": 404190.0,
      "text": "but does it for those who are yet to find their voices."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 407197.0,
      "end_time": 412470.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 414901.0,
      "end_time": 418845.0,
      "text": "My seizures are greatly reduced, from two to three times a day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 418869.0,
      "end_time": 422276.0,
      "text": "to sometimes two to three times in one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 422300.0,
      "end_time": 423510.0,
      "text": "I went on --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 423534.0,
      "end_time": 427498.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 429299.0,
      "end_time": 431902.0,
      "text": "I went on to employ five people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 431927.0,
      "end_time": 434188.0,
      "text": "when I began what was Kenya&#39;s first"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 434212.0,
      "end_time": 437289.0,
      "text": "free mental health and epilepsy support line."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 437682.0,
      "end_time": 439400.0,
      "text": "And I travel --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 439280.0,
      "end_time": 441325.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 441349.0,
      "end_time": 445847.0,
      "text": "And I travel to speak about my affair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 445871.0,
      "end_time": 448228.0,
      "text": "all these things that I had been told"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 448252.0,
      "end_time": 452609.0,
      "text": "people like me living with epilepsy could never be able to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 453110.0,
      "end_time": 458326.0,
      "text": "Every year, a population as big as 80 percent of Nairobi"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 458350.0,
      "end_time": 461115.0,
      "text": "gets diagnosed with epilepsy"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 461139.0,
      "end_time": 462578.0,
      "text": "across the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 463166.0,
      "end_time": 464325.0,
      "text": "And they, like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 464349.0,
      "end_time": 469279.0,
      "text": "go through the emotions of stigma and exclusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 470422.0,
      "end_time": 473898.0,
      "text": "And so I have made it my life journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 473922.0,
      "end_time": 476506.0,
      "text": "to keep these conversations going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 476530.0,
      "end_time": 479705.0,
      "text": "and I keep confessing about my affair"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 479729.0,
      "end_time": 483820.0,
      "text": "so that those people who do not have the diagnosis"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 483107.0,
      "end_time": 487440.0,
      "text": "might know and might have a constant reminder"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 487680.0,
      "end_time": 490248.0,
      "text": "that it is alright to engage with people like us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 490272.0,
      "end_time": 495832.0,
      "text": "that as long as they pull down the walls of stigma and exclusion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 495856.0,
      "end_time": 498730.0,
      "text": "that we, just like them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 498970.0,
      "end_time": 501777.0,
      "text": "can be able to take anything life throws at us."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
